title: You are now in control of Grand RP!
content:
It seems I have witnessed some secret information. For an entire month, I've been secretly watching the Developers work on the update and carefully been passing along information about what players like you and me want to change.

Racing

Many players like me love to race. Now every hour on the server automatically starts a new race. A total of 15 unique tracks have been added, each with a different style and difficulty. The main feature is, it’s a full randomisation. Each race is launched on a random track, and you never know where you will end up: in the city centre, in the desert or even in the air.

A new system for families “State Control”.

State Control is a brand new turf system for families. It starts simple - you and your family pick a starting point on the edge of the map. From there you begin a step-by-step progression, square by square, building your chain of influence. The goal is to reach strategically important objects: warehouses, businesses, and sometimes even rare event points. But the path won't be easy. Each square can become the arena of a real battle, because other families are doing the same.

These and many other changes are already available on Grand RP!
If you are not interested

By the way, I decided to let you know because you play on RP Grand and registered there. If you're not interested, just let me know.
